{"tid":1199781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"100萬人出嚟但仍然有好多人仲繼續做港豬","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:12:36.000Z","uid":213699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"942992b06c26592836c8e58aa955c7eda04781e1","tid":1199781,"uid":213699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"話尻人淨係識打卡唔衝<br />\n首先唔好話衝唔衝<br />\n點解打卡一啲用都無？遊行不嬲都係一傳十 十傳百唔係邊得嚟今次一百萬人出嚟<br />\n唔係邊得嚟咁多人留意番多啲政治<br />\n點解仲要坐喺冷氣房懶獨特扮晒看透世事 知道發生咩事就夠<br />\n事實就係你根撚本就係港豬<br />\n次次都唔出 有事先算 到真正有事仲有邊個會出<br />\n無人會可憐你架<br />\n<br />\n同埋個個淨係識結果論<br />\n咩一早知遊行又點 政府一定唔會理尻你<br />\n屌你老母結果論我都做到賭神啦<br />\n喂 每次出嚟都係一次嘅賭博 <br />\n我知我買緊嘅野係一賠99<br />\n我知道贏嘅機會係好微<br />\n但我知道我唔買就一定會輸<br />\n我希望你地明白"},{"pid":"edaf3f1a234125408ef5928c6cff8e8285a09144","tid":1199781,"uid":8290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b44b22b5e7f82e8a1f9e70c303a1ba1d92143f","tid":1199781,"uid":213699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edaf3f1a234125408ef5928c6cff8e8285a09144","tid":1199781,"uid":8290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8277ecd874cfdd97746be6123f5f78aeb0bee20","tid":1199781,"uid":213699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406878f662def034f5661aadc24df36b9598dd14","tid":1199781,"uid":213699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.